{"id":17,"date":"2013-08-07T17:24:06","date_gmt":"2013-08-07T15:24:06","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/smit.co.za\/?p=17"},"modified":"2022-05-12T20:55:03","modified_gmt":"2022-05-12T18:55:03","slug":"vlugbal-2002","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/vlugbal-2002\/","title":{"rendered":"Vlugbal 2002"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Vlugbal 2002 was my last Computer Studies project in my final year of High School.<\/p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a hotseat multiplayer volleybal game written in <a title=\"Turbo Pascal \" href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Turbo_Pascal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Turbo Pascal<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/vlugbal-2002.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-20  aligncenter\" alt=\"Gameplay Vlugbal 2002\" src=\"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/vlugbal-2002.png\" width=\"459\" height=\"363\" srcset=\"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/vlugbal-2002.png 656w, https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/vlugbal-2002-300x237.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 459px) 100vw, 459px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>We had to design a piece of software that had some visual components, writes\/reads to a file and contains the normal\u00a0programming\u00a0statements (for loops + if else etc). It uses the PC speaker for sound.<\/p>\n<p>It also includes a 3D rendered intro video for the game, you can <a title=\"Vlugbal 2002 video\" href=\"https:\/\/www.smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/Vlugbal2002\/Vlugbal2002 intro.avi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">download the video directly from here<\/a>. \u00a0It was made in 3D studio Max, and it took 20 hours to render on our 333mhz Celeron.\u00a0(Personally think the intro is better than the game itself)<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_19\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-19\" style=\"width: 462px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/intro-screenshot-Vlugbal-2002.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-19\" alt=\"Vlugbal 2002 screenshot of video\" src=\"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/intro-screenshot-Vlugbal-2002.png\" width=\"462\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/intro-screenshot-Vlugbal-2002.png 462w, https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/intro-screenshot-Vlugbal-2002-300x220.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 462px) 100vw, 462px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-19\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vlugbal 2002 screenshot of video<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go ahead and download the <a title=\"Vlugbal 2002 installation\" href=\"https:\/\/www.smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/Vlugbal2002\/Vlugbal2002(watch_intro_in_installed_folder).exe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vlugbal 2002 installation file<\/a>, it contains the source code as well. \u00a0The intro video doesn&#8217;t automatically play in operating systems after Windows 98, but you can find it in the install directory.<\/p>\n<p>If you have Windows XP or newer installed, you will need\u00a0to install <a title=\"DosBox\" href=\"https:\/\/sourceforge.net\/projects\/dosbox\/files\/latest\/download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DosBox <\/a>first before you can play the game. So install Dosbox, run it, then you have to mount and run game like so in dosbox :<\/p>\n<p>[quote]mount c: &#8220;C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Vlugbal 2002&#8221;<br \/>\nc:\\<br \/>\ngame.exe[\/quote]<\/p>\n<p>The <a title=\"Help document\" href=\"https:\/\/www.smit.co.za\/wp-content\/uploads\/vlugbal2002\/Vinnige handleiding.doc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">help file<\/a> (Handleiding) contains help information in Afrikaans<\/p>\n<p>Hope you enjoy this very simple game<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vlugbal 2002 was my last Computer Studies project in my final year of High School. It&#8217;s a hotseat multiplayer volleybal game written in Turbo Pascal. We had to design a piece of software that had some visual components, writes\/reads to a file and contains the normal\u00a0programming\u00a0statements (for loops + if else etc). It uses the&hellip; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/vlugbal-2002\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Vlugbal 2002<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3,10],"tags":[12,14,15,16,13],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17"}],"version-history":[{"count":20,"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":198,"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17\/revisions\/198"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/smit.co.za\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}